d":1086913,"uid":243588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"352e0e00796ea701624384c61bea23b346a660fe","tid":1086913,"uid":46480,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T08:59:57.000Z","msg":"其實有啲真係會知<br />\n依家有個女仔，佢有男朋友，佢話佢男朋友之前有求婚但無應承，佢想同我一齊<br />\n家底上，佢屋企做生意住半山，平日成日去啲ball會，佢想叫埋我去，但我覺得我去到果啲場合係on99咁<br />\n佢識既人咩都有，外國人，唔同年紀，佢屋企啲生意朋友<br />\n佢係靚女喺街都有人問攞電話果種，佢對啲追佢既人唔會明確拒絕，係會keep住同人做朋友關係<br />\n佢既屋企正正常常，關係好好，又外向多朋友果種<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我，普通舊式單橦私樓家庭，老豆過左身，屋企關係普通，同屋企人無野好傾果種<br />\n栍格本身係內向少朋友，時間主要係同女朋友一齊<br />\n平日食野，興趣，去既地方完全同佢唔同<br />\n而且大家愛情上既價值觀差好遠<br />\n我係保守，佢係開放<br />\n如果一齊左，我都好驚佢遇到下個之後會好似對佢男朋友咁對我<br />\n<br />\n大家依家27-28，講真過幾年已經係結婚年齡，我應該係比唔到佢想要既生活比佢<br />\n我唔想中左埋去，2-3年後，因為啲現實既問題而分開<br />\n對佢黎講佢有本錢，又靚又有家底當然無問題<br />\n但係我真係已經玩唔起了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"振作吖 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"明明好鐘意，但要逼自己推開佢<br />\n唔知佢明唔明我點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:28:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母本身有女朋友？"},{"pid":"43897eaf8d2d86f6bd29e21f58b1c787179567ad","tid":1086913,"uid":46480,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e466ad3766f950297964ec026a5e83e166bccddb","tid":1086913,"uid":240150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5eea2bc689ad5884bc147779e4936fd4d506071","tid":1086913,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7447043d28b79eee1cb2d6ef89a737a630b5cc9c","tid":1086913,"uid":243588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:39:11.000Z","msg":"振作吖 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"明明好鐘意，但要逼自己推開佢<br />\n唔知佢明唔明我點解要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:28:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母本身有女朋友？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:34:20.000Z","msg":"yes, 我係仆街<br />\n但呢個都係其中一個我要推開佢既原因<br />\n因為我知大家有另一半咁開始<br />\n最後唔會有好結果<br />\n<br />\n你話我精神出軌又好點都好<br />\n我只係講返我依家真實既感覺<br />\n雖然係鐘意佢<br />\n但逼自己諗只係新鮮感<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea06e89f02fdda0d4f3c6d340f9373283da6b216","tid":1086913,"uid":209724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:50:04.000Z","msg":"咁多戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91289c1fcf57d1c9e78c84db8e7fc2bd5444ceab","tid":1086913,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea06e89f02fdda0d4f3c6d340f9373283da6b216","tid":1086913,"uid":209724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:50:04.000Z","msg":"咁多戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"係咪後生無顧慮既都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b573189f1eeaa6d3d349f8dda66df600b3bb877","tid":1086913,"uid":200440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:17:11.000Z","msg":"我都覺得如果冇將來咁不如唔好開始<br />\n甚至拍拖個陣開始意識到兩個唔會行到落去嘅時候就會提出分手，因為覺得無謂浪費大家時間，不如早啲分開反而冇咁hurt，唔知自己係太理性定太冷漠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172e917a1e648f434038afbaba63de8d6f536356","tid":1086913,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b573189f1eeaa6d3d349f8dda66df600b3bb877","tid":1086913,"uid":200440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:17:11.000Z","msg":"我都覺得如果冇將來咁不如唔好開始<br />\n甚至拍拖個陣開始意識到兩個唔會行到落去嘅時候就會提出分手，因為覺得無謂浪費大家時間，不如早啲分開反而冇咁hurt，唔知自己係太理性定太冷漠<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:25:43.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗<br />\n拖得愈耐<br />\n感情愈深<br />\n分開既時候就愈hurt<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nhurt多幾次就覺得自己好難再全心去鐘意一個人了"},{"pid":"ebeee68ddc1dc3a7e278d741d95286e152ed6dad","tid":1086913,"uid":121966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:56:30.000Z","msg":"我係後者 涯左兩年 我同佢唔同世界<br />\n我明白佢 但佢唔明白我<br />\n我一直都忍讓 結果都係唔夠 <br />\n最後分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14aa05636aa0b967fc755bd68a24bedab431ce9f","tid":1086913,"uid":121966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebeee68ddc1dc3a7e278d741d95286e152ed6dad","tid":1086913,"uid":121966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:56:30.000Z","msg":"我係後者 涯左兩年 我同佢唔同世界<br />\n我明白佢 但佢唔明白我<br />\n我一直都忍讓 結果都係唔夠 <br />\n最後分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:59:37.000Z","msg":"佢話我做得唔好 我又覺得佢無體諒我有情緒病<br />\n佢同時又有情緒病 本身我無 做我咩起左佢人生兩年<br />\n最後我支持唔住都病左 之後佢罵我好負面 想放棄我<br />\n但又無分手 之後所有野就現形 所有唔適合既野 所有野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85774123e408811f6b490d09027b2f183b73269b","tid":1086913,"uid":121966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"14aa05636aa0b967fc755bd68a24bedab431ce9f","tid":1086913,"uid":121966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebeee68ddc1dc3a7e278d741d95286e152ed6dad","tid":1086913,"uid":121966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:56:30.000Z","msg":"我係後者 涯左兩年 我同佢唔同世界<br />\n我明白佢 但佢唔明白我<br />\n我一直都忍讓 結果都係唔夠 <br />\n最後分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T12:59:37.000Z","msg":"佢話我做得唔好 我又覺得佢無體諒我有情緒病<br />\n佢同時又有情緒病 本身我無 做我咩起左佢人生兩年<br />\n最後我支持唔住都病左 之後佢罵我好負面 想放棄我<br />\n但又無分手 之後所有野就現形 所有唔適合既野 所有野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T13:01:03.000Z","msg":"我想同大家講既係<br />\n第一下去做去諗未試過點知個陣<br />\n可能你會被愛充昏頭腦 覺得好愛佢 好熱血青春或者點<br />\n但一耐左 一齊耐左之後 熱戀期後 先係真正既開始"},{"pid":"05b4c62f75c1cfe602cc479e57876a8be5f47a54","tid":1086913,"uid":209724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91289c1fcf57d1c9e78c84db8e7fc2bd5444ceab","tid":1086913,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea06e89f02fdda0d4f3c6d340f9373283da6b216","tid":1086913,"uid":209724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:50:04.000Z","msg":"咁多戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"係咪後生無顧慮既都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"屌俾你講中左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人大左拍拖邊有咁簡單"},{"pid":"a089128b193e49d53771e5eb5649c2fd3ae71246","tid":1086913,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"05b4c62f75c1cfe602cc479e57876a8be5f47a54","tid":1086913,"uid":209724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"91289c1fcf57d1c9e78c84db8e7fc2bd5444ceab","tid":1086913,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea06e89f02fdda0d4f3c6d340f9373283da6b216","tid":1086913,"uid":209724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:50:04.000Z","msg":"咁多戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"係咪後生無顧慮既都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T13:24:59.000Z","msg":"屌俾你講中左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人大左拍拖邊有咁簡單"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"有時都驚撞到呢類人<br />\n佢會令你覺得大家真係可以overcome到啲問題行到最後<br />\n比佢感染到自己都沖昏左頭腦<br />\n點知一齊之後發現其實佢一開始係根本無預過有啲咩問題會出現<br />\n到時一係大家累鬥累<br />\n一係佢拉左你落去之後自己就話都係唔適合然後拍拍羅柚走左去<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3e5325b6d97caf944bd17bb2e1251ac2f6802d","tid":1086913,"uid":202525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T15:24:12.000Z","msg":"比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />既人都係擔心太多冇咩安全感<br />\n<br />\n利申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ed <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}